            "title": "聯儲局官員稱關稅一對一替代 經濟展望不變",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"聯儲局官員稱關稅一對一替代 經濟展望不變\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"640\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/qJxRUe_FhqZ5E5pVDl7d.A--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MA--/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2025-02/09b3e130-efb4-11ef-8db3-eac75891d0c3\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">聯儲局官員稱關稅一對一替代 經濟展望不變</figcaption></div></figure></div>",
